Package: forestkit
Type: Package
Title: Publication-Quality Forest and Dose-Response Spline Figures
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mohamadjavad", "Ershadmanesh", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "dr.mjershad@gmail.com")
Description: Two figure helpers for meta-analysis output: pub_forest() draws a
    forest plot with an optional pooled diamond, and dose_spline() fits and
    plots a restricted cubic spline dose-response curve. Both write a 300-dpi
    PNG plus a vector PDF, and both write the underlying numbers to CSV before
    opening the graphics device so a render failure never loses the results.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    grDevices,
    graphics,
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
    rms,
    splines
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
